{"tid":1198587,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[來了]韋智達律師行支持員工「憑良心行事」罷工","createTime":"2019-06-10T09:29:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T09:34:55.000Z","uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9be9c228cb4848032a3b805053266bac9f6dd7c5","tid":1198587,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:29:23.000Z","msg":"民陣昨發起遊行，反對修訂《逃犯條例》，稱有103萬人參加，特區政府其後發稿表示，修例草案會如期在星期三（12日）恢復二讀，有網民發起周三罷工。曾協助一度滯港沙特阿拉伯姊妹的韋智達律師行（Vidler &amp; Co. Solicitors）表示，員工若「想憑良心行事」，於當日因參與罷工而缺勤，律師行會予以支持。<br />\n<br />\n律師行指出，為維持對當事人的服務並履行對法院的職責，會在辦公時間如常開放辦公室，並由律師行主事人韋智達律師維持服務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190610/s00001/1560158275915/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190610%2Fs00001%2F1560158275915%2F&d=AePTNAtL1N4PdcNq2S6jCKwVmkNCIo3TbJkxuaymrXU%3D&h=1148d2cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190610%2Fs00001%2F1560158275915%2F&h=7a7ae8bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190610/s00001/1560158275915/</a>"},{"pid":"610c82d96bcc18f624c24d112471c511d95a5e77","tid":1198587,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:34:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}